dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents tax parcels for Brown County, Wisconsin in 2012. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Brown_Parcels_2012.gdb.
uw_supplemental_s: This metadata was updated in fall of 2017 to reflect that the data is no longer restricted and has been opened for public use.Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit https://www.co.brown.wi.us/departments/?department=85713eda4cdc
